FBIS4-2922 "drchi073_h_94001" FBIS-CHI-94-073 Daily Report 14 Apr 1994 West Europe Portuguese Prime Minister Tours Shanghai 14 Apr Portuguese Prime Minister Tours Shanghai 14 Apr OW1404145794 Beijing XINHUA in English 1428 GMT 14 Apr 94 OW1404145794 Beijing XINHUA English BFN [Text] Shanghai, April 14 (XINHUA) -- Visiting Portuguese Prime Minister Anibal Cavaco Silva, accompanied by Liu Xiliang, chairman of Chinese Government Reception Committee and vice-minister of radio, film and television, toured Minhang Economic and Technological Development Zone and a village in the western part of Shanghai this morning. Silva and his party arrived here from Beijing by special plane yesterday. Vice-Mayor Xu Kuangdi of Shanghai, on behalf of Mayor Huang Ju, met with Silva last night. Silva said during the meeting that his country would like to contribute to the economic development of shanghai. Portuguese entrepreneurs accompanying Silva on his China tour held talks with their counterparts from Shanghai this afternoon. Silva and his party left Shanghai by special plane for Hangzhou, capital of East China's Zhejiang Province.
